com.tangosol.util

Class SafeSortedMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentSkipListMap
        • com.tangosol.util.SafeSortedMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, ConcurrentMap, ConcurrentNavigableMap, Map, NavigableMap, SortedMap

    public class SafeSortedMap
extends ConcurrentSkipListMap
    Implementation of a SortedMap extending ConcurrentSkipListMap to support null keys and null values. Note that unlike its super class, this class is not serializable.
    Since:
    23.03
    Author:
    mg
